<!-- PAGE HERO -->
<section class="page-hero">
<div class="container">
<div class="page-hero-inner">
<div class="slabel">Private Patient Fees &amp; Pricing</div>
<h1>Understanding the Cost of Your Private Treatment</h1>
<p>Mr Hussain treats both self-pay and insured patients at Woodlands Suite (Royal Orthopaedic Hospital), Harborne Hospital, and Priory Hospital Edgbaston. All fees include a personalised care plan and direct access to Mr Hussain throughout your journey.</p>
<div class="page-hero-badges">
  <div class="hero-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Self-Pay &amp; Insured Patients</div>
  <div class="hero-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Pre-authorisation Support</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- CONSULTATION FEES -->
<section class="consult-fees" id="consultations">
<div class="container">
<div style="text-align:center">
