<!-- SELF-PAY & INSURER GUIDE -->
<section class="selfpay" id="self-pay">
<div class="container">
<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0">
  <div class="slabel">Your Options Explained</div>
  <h2 class="stitle">Self-Pay &amp; Insured Patients</h2>
</div>
<div class="selfpay-grid">
  <div class="selfpay-col">
    <h3>Paying for Yourself (Self-Pay)</h3>
    <p>Many patients choose to pay privately for faster access, greater choice of surgeon, and a more personalised experience. Self-pay is simpler than it might seem:</p>
    <ol class="step-list">
      <li><div><strong>Book your initial consultation</strong> &mdash; Contact Wendy Richards, Mr Hussain&rsquo;s secretary, to arrange your first appointment.</div></li>
      <li><div><strong>Receive your personalised plan</strong> &mdash; Mr Hussain will assess you and, if surgery is recommended, provide a fixed all-inclusive quote.</div></li>
      <li><div><strong>Confirm your procedure date</strong> &mdash; Surgery is typically available within weeks. You pay the agreed package fee before your operation.</div></li>
      <li><div><strong>Recover with confidence</strong> &mdash; All follow-up appointments are included. Mr Hussain&rsquo;s team supports you every step of the way.</div></li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <div class="selfpay-col">
    <h3>Using Health Insurance</h3>
    <p>Mr Hussain is recognised by all major UK health insurers. Before booking, contact your insurer to obtain a pre-authorisation number. We will handle the rest.</p>
    <p>Please confirm with your insurer:</p>
    <div class="insurance-grid">
      <div class="ins-tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Your level of cover for orthopaedic surgery</div>
      <div class="ins-tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Whether a GP referral letter is required</div>
      <div class="ins-tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Any excess payments on your policy</div>
      <div class="ins-tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Whether Mr Hussain is on their approved list</div>
      <div class="ins-tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Cover for your chosen hospital</div>
      <div class="ins-tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Your pre-authorisation reference number</div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:24px;font-size:.95rem;color:#5a5a5a;line-height:1.8;background:#f0efeb;padding:20px;border-radius:8px;border-left:3px solid #c5a44e"><strong style="color:#0c1f3f">Need help?</strong> Wendy Richards, Mr Hussain&rsquo;s dedicated secretary, is on hand to assist with insurance queries and pre-authorisation. Call or email to discuss your situation before your appointment.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

